headline.print_headline: Kerber Overcomes Blip to Beat Local Hope Gajdosova
headline.main: Kerber Overcomes Blip to Beat Local Hope Gajdosova

lead_paragraph: Ninth-seed Angelique Kerber shook off a second-set blip to advance to the second round of the Australian Open on Monday with a 6-3 0-6 6-2 win over local wildcard Jarmila Gajdosova.
